CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 3, 1956, pg. B5 reads: "Hostesses at the Achievement Club reception were members of the junior group of New Kensington. They are Mary Vining, Carol Taylor, Barbara Clements, Theresa Miles and Naomi Coates. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Achievement Club reception hostesses, including: Mary Vining, Carol Taylor, Barbara Clements, Theresa Miles, and Naomi Coates, posed behind table in YWCA with abstract curtains
